{"tid":1492703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如文宣主力宣傳 （登報）共產黨正式成為納粹黨","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T07:07:04.000Z","uid":2719,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aac1c93706bff0f4dca004b03209d339c090898d","tid":1492703,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"1. 新疆集中營<br />\n2. 去人化 - 稱示威者為曱甴<br />\n3. 控制言論帶風向<br />\n4. 白色恐怖<br />\n5. 擴大版圖 - 高息一帶一路令弱國無錢還領土<br />\n6. 大逃殺 - 室內和高空放催淚彈<br />\n7. 無差別殘酷殺人 - 槍/催淚彈/狗棍(鑲鐵環)<br />\n<br />\n我一次過列晒所有仆街野，<br />\n我知有啲唔係納粹，再執。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">納粹先會挑起外國人神經</span></span><br />\n我地登香港示威，佢地最多心入面覺得慘，支持。<br />\n你地要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">狂提曱甴</span></span>等納粹主義，<br />\n佢地先會真上心，希望文宣努力。<br />\n我文盲幫唔到寫，但我會捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cb91214e64de7e257ff729ce4a34cd15ff7b90","tid":1492703,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xO2XB3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxO2XB3w.jpg&h=077c7acc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cf57a0db6ea8332e70de125450c9e956d996e11","tid":1492703,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"baaaddfb0c7d906716e1888982ffc497ad921809","tid":1492703,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:10:09.000Z","msg":"仲有班支拿人係外國納綷式拍手"},{"pid":"1ac5fa53d27f844bae561ee14573a18c8f6e2bf1","tid":1492703,"uid":5047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b0209e74f1dac974789e6a5c0172eaa095c640","tid":1492703,"uid":32147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"推<img